  "remarks": "\nNational Assembly Deputy (2021-26), member of the NA’s Committee of the Preliminary Commission of Electoral Nominations and Vice President of the Permanent Commission of the Family. Former Member of the illegitimate National Constituent Assembly since August 2017, and former Second Vice President since October 2018. Her actions as part of the National Constituent Assembly (ANC) including signing the decree that stripped the immunity of the president of the National Assembly (AN) and the interim-President of Venezuela, Juan Guaido, have undermined democracy and rule of law in Venezuela.  \n",
